17:05.816 --> 17:07.483
You're not just trying
to please me by saying this?

17:07.568 --> 17:09.944
And I wish I could give her the software

17:10.029 --> 17:10.988
to get her back, but...

17:14.156 --> 17:15.284
it's... it's fake.

17:16.285 --> 17:18.078
I knew it. I knew it.

17:18.829 --> 17:19.954
She's not over me?

17:20.497 --> 17:23.165
No, Fakeblock. It's fake.

17:25.502 --> 17:28.005
