18:34.655 --> 18:36.698
Well, has anyone checked under the...

18:38.325 --> 18:39.493
new bailiff?

18:40.077 --> 18:42.746
- Gene Parmesan.
- Gene!

18:42.830 --> 18:44.123
And I swear to tell the truth,

18:44.206 --> 18:47.167
- so help me God.
- That never gets old!

18:47.626 --> 18:49.962
I'll tell you something else
that never gets old. Whoops.

18:50.045 --> 18:51.463
I'm under oath.

18:53.882 --> 18:55.968
- On the night of Cinco de Cuatro...
- Yeah.

18:56.051 --> 18:58.428
...you were undercover,
working selling donkey punch.

18:58.512 --> 19:00.097
- Isn't that correct?
- Definitely undercover.

19:00.180 --> 19:02.182
I don't need two jobs.

19:02.266 --> 19:04.017
'Cause everything's going really good.

19:04.101 --> 19:05.644
What exactly is in a donkey punch?

19:05.727 --> 19:07.146
You know, mostly Kool-Aid.

19:07.229 --> 19:09.481
- So it's similar to juice, then?
