19:10.399 --> 19:11.817
<i>Lucille was concerned.</i>

19:11.900 --> 19:14.486
<i>The DA appeared to have done
her homework on Buster</i>

19:14.570 --> 19:18.949
<i>and his lack of restraint
under the influence of sugary juice.</i>

19:19.032 --> 19:21.326
<i>And she found herself resenting a man</i>

19:21.410 --> 19:23.036
<i>- she'd once admired.</i>
- Your witness.

19:23.120 --> 19:25.372
<i>But Lottie stopped short</i>
<i>of making that point.</i>

19:25.455 --> 19:26.999
Do you want me to take it easy on him?

19:27.082 --> 19:29.209
Or give it to him hard?
