22:38.607 --> 22:40.942
Gosh, I don't really know
if we need any acting right now.

22:41.568 --> 22:44.404
The stuff we're doing here,
it's more about preventing hacking,

22:44.488 --> 22:47.824
- protecting privacy, and stuff like that.
