25:58.848 --> 26:02.811
<i>- We haven't licensed most of this music.</i>
- What? What do you think you're doing?

26:03.144 --> 26:05.730
I told you. I'm taking this girl who,
in my opinion,

26:05.814 --> 26:07.440
has been mistreated by you
for far too long

26:07.524 --> 26:09.609
on a cruise with her grandmother.

26:09.693 --> 26:11.528
You're not taking her anywhere.

26:12.153 --> 26:13.572
Oh, come on, Mom.

26:13.905 --> 26:15.699
I <i>am </i> almost 14,

26:15.782 --> 26:18.702
- and you <i>have </i> been mistreating me.
- Oh...

26:19.327 --> 26:20.579
You go to your room.

26:22.998 --> 26:24.749
How dare you?

26:24.833 --> 26:27.294
We both know that child
is about to turn 18.

26:27.377 --> 26:29.963
- Oh, that's right, it slipped my mind.
- Oh, please.

26:30.046 --> 26:33.008
That's all you've been thinking about
since you put her up for adoption.

26:33.091 --> 26:34.884
<i>It hasn't been on your mind?</i>

26:36.428 --> 26:38.555
You swooped in and stole her
from the Standwells

26:38.638 --> 26:39.931
when you found out about the endowment,

26:40.015 --> 26:43.184
'cause you just had to have
a cottage on the beach.

26:44.394 --> 26:46.104
You can say goodbye to that, honey.

26:46.396 --> 26:47.606
Because that child is mine,

26:47.689 --> 26:49.899
and I have nothing else
in my life right now.

26:49.983 --> 26:51.526
<i>And I'm not gonna spend
the rest of it singing</i>

26:51.610 --> 26:53.445
<i>on a cruise ship for snifter tips.</i>

26:53.862 --> 26:55.447
<i>I knew this is</i>
<i>what you were up to.</i>

26:55.530 --> 26:57.240
Suddenly, there's no gentleman caller
in the picture,

26:57.324 --> 26:59.117
and you decide to look out for yourself?

26:59.200 --> 27:01.536
Oh, you're one to talk
about looking out for yourself.

27:01.620 --> 27:04.164
I've never been invited
to this place even once,

27:04.247 --> 27:05.749
and let's not forget who paid for it.

27:06.583 --> 27:08.752
And this is how
you want to be paid back?

27:08.835 --> 27:11.713
You think you're gonna walk
in here and take away my child?

27:11.796 --> 27:14.174
